name: SupplierShipPurchaseOrder
description:
Ships a Purchase Order with specified lines. Supply either `ID` or a `BackendID`/`BackendSystemID` combination to
identify the order.

If you wish to receive on behalf of a different organization, identify that organization by specifying a
`ShipToOrganizationUnitBackendID`. Should this organization reside in a different cluster, this call will be proxied
to that cluster for you.
